lead_paragraph: Olympic ski cross bronze medallist Anna Holmlund of Sweden was put in a medically-induced coma after sustaining a head injury in a training accident in Italy, Scandinavian media reported on Monday.

headline.print_headline: Swedish Skier Holmlund in Coma After Training Crash
